 competition from consulting firms and major platforms, impacting market share as of 2024.", 'company_briefing': 'ADKマーケティングソリューションズ is a solutions company that provides integrated marketing solutions for clients seeking to solve marketing challenges.\n\n### Core Product/Service\n* Offers digital advertising solutions.\n* Provides mass advertising solutions.\n* Provides direct marketing solutions.\n* Offers customer data and insights services.\n* Offers customer experience design services.\n* Provides customer contact management services.\n* Offers integrated solutions across departments and job types.\n* Utilizes BI/AI technologies for marketing support.\n* Utilizes DMP/CDP technologies for marketing support.\n* Utilizes MA/CRM technologies for marketing support.\n* Employs a persona creation tool using generative AI, named "エモグラ".\n\n### Leadership Team\n* Toshiya Oyama is the Representative Director and President.\n* Mamoru Sanda is a Director and Executive Officer overseeing Business Produce.\n* Tetsuya Hisano is a Director.\n* Kenji Mochizuki is a Director and Executive Officer overseeing Media Business.\n* Yoichi Machida is a Director and Group Executive Officer CFO.\n* Takashi Zempo is a Director.\n* Haruyuki Shimizu is an Auditor.\n* Yoshihiko Tonomura is an Auditor.\n\n### Target Market\n* Targets client companies across various industries.\n* Supports client marketing organizations through design and operational support.\n* Aims to generate fans and deepen bonds with them, fostering new value for business growth.\n* Contributes to clients\' business success by providing valuable customer experiences.\n* Supports D2C (Direct to Consumer) communications between businesses and consumers.\n* Offers integrated solutions, including mass and digital strategies.\n\n### Key Differentiators\n* Offers unique solutions combining mass and digital approaches.\n* Provides integrated communication strategies across full funnels.\n* Delivers client-first proposals, diverging from traditional mass advertising agency logic.\n* Employs a one-team approach across digital and mass advertising departments.\n* Integrates digital methods into television advertising planning and buying.\n* Offers "Brand Boost Method" composed of:文脈資産型コミュニケーション，界隈マーケティング，未来クリエイティブ.\n### Business Model\n* Offers solutions across diverse digital-era customer touchpoints like social, EC, and CRM.\n* Provides full-funnel marketing strategies, not just conversion-focused tactics.\n* Pricing is based on providing integrated solutions that connect client issues to optimal solutions.\n* Offers services through a one-roof integrated solution service brand called ADK CONNECT.\n* Distributes solutions through a unified team of experts in digital and mass advertising.', 'references': ['https://www.adkms.jp', 'https://www.adkms.jp/business', 'https://www.adkms.jp/company/profile', 'https://www.adk.jp/news', 'https://www.adk.jp/about/outline', 'https://macloud.jp/companies/471', 'https://www.adk.jp/en/about/outline', 'https://www.adkms.jp/news/20241223-2', 'https://www.adk.jp/news/109207', 'https://lifedoctor-campus.com/company-study/entry/koukokudairiten/study-adk.html'], 'briefings': {'financial': '### Funding & Investment\n*   Bain Capital acquired ADK Group in 2017.\n\n### Revenue Model\n*   Offers integrated marketing solutions.\n*   Provides digital and mass media planning and buying services.\n*   Offers data-driven marketing services.', 'news': '### Major Announcements\n*   2025.05.15 ADKマーケティング・ソリューションズ、ブランド開発などをサポートしたキリンホールディングスの「エレ…\n*   2025.04.03 ADKグループ、生成AIを活用したペルソナ作成ツール「エモグラ」を開発\n*   2024.12.20 ADKマーケティング・ソリューションズ、スタートアップ企業のバリューアップを支援する「ADKスタートアップ・ブースト・スタジオ」のサービス提供を開始\n*   2024.12.20 「全国メディアプロフィールサーベイ2024」を提供開始\n*   2024.12.19 ADKマーケティング・ソリューションズ、「ゲーム総合調査レポート2024」を発表\u3000～最新のゲーム市況の把握から、ゲームプレイヤーの行動・心理の分析まで網羅～\n*   2024.12.16 ADKマーケティング・ソリューションズ、「ADK生活者総合調査2024」より 『SDGsに関する意識結果』を発表\n*   2024.11.27 ADKワカスタ、ワカモノならではの視点で企業課題を解決する マーケティングアイデアコンテスト、『ワカスタ ビジコン 2024