ing mass and digital strategies.\n\n### Key Differentiators\n* Offers unique solutions combining mass and digital approaches.\n* Provides integrated communication strategies across full funnels.\n* Delivers client-first proposals, diverging from traditional mass advertising agency logic.\n* Employs a one-team approach across digital and mass advertising departments.\n* Integrates digital methods into television advertising planning and buying.\n* Offers "Brand Boost Method" composed of:文脈資産型コミュニケーション，界隈マーケティング，未来クリエイティブ.\n### Business Model\n* Offers solutions across diverse digital-era customer touchpoints like social, EC, and CRM.\n* Provides full-funnel marketing strategies, not just conversion-focused tactics.\n* Pricing is based on providing integrated solutions that connect client issues to optimal solutions.\n* Offers services through a one-roof integrated solution service brand called ADK CONNECT.\n* Distributes solutions through a unified team of experts in digital and mass advertising.'}}
